---
import Layout from '../components/layout/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="Learn more about my background, skills, and journey in software engineering."
>
  <div class="container section">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto ml-5">
      <!-- Header -->
      <header class="mb-12 animate-fade-in">
        <h1 class="font-mono text-3xl font-bold mb-2">About Me</h1>
        <p class="font-sans text-md text-secondary">
          My journey in software engineering and technology
        </p>
      </header>

      <!-- Main Content -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <!-- Introduction -->
        <section class="animate-fade-in delay-1">
          <div class="card">
            <h2 class="font-mono text-xl font-bold mb-3">Hello, I'm Anbu Thuran!</h2>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <p class="font-sans text-base text-secondary leading-normal">
                I’m a software engineer focused on building reliable backend systems and thoughtful solutions. My primary stack is Java and Spring Boot, with experience in React, and I’m actively expanding into TypeScript and Next.js.
                I have also worked on RAG, Agentic AI Systems, designing structured, explainable agents and multi-agent workflows that can integrate in enterprise environments.
                I write technical articles from time to time, and working on projects that prioritize fundamentals.
              </p>
              <p class="font-sans text-base text-secondary leading-normal">
                My journey in technology began during my college years with a curiosity about how things work and evolved into
                a career building software that impacts users worldwide. I believe in writing clean,
                maintainable code.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Background & Education -->
        <section class="animate-fade-in delay-3">
          <h2 class="font-mono text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Background & Education</h2>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="mb-4">
              <h3 class="font-mono text-lg font-bold mb-1">Bachelor of Engineering in Computer Science</h3>
              <p class="font-mono text-base mb-1" style="color: var(--color-accent);">
                Bannari Amman Institute of Technology - CGPA : 8.9 / 10
              </p>
              <p class="font-mono text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">2020 - 2024</p>
            </div>
            <p class="font-sans text-base" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: 1.5;">
              During my time at university, I developed a strong foundation in computer science
              fundamentals including algorithms, data structures, operating systems, and software
              engineering. I also participated in competitions and hackathons while working on projects.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="animate-fade-in delay-2">
          <h2 class="font-mono text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Interests & Values</h2>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
            <div class="card">
              <h3 class="font-mono text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-accent);">
                Problem Solving
              </h3>
              <p class="font-sans text-base" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: 1.5;">
                I have a strong love for solving problems, data structures and algorithms. I have solved over 500 problems on <a href="https://leetcode.com/u/tanbumails/">Leetcode</a>. Even during my college days, I have always participated in coding competitions.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <h3 class="font-mono text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-accent);">
                AI
              </h3>
              <p class="font-sans text-base" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: 1.5;">
                I like to stay up to date with emerging technologies and experiment with them hands-on.
                Recently, I’ve been exploring Claude Code, building AI agents, skills, and structured workflows rather than simple prompt-based systems. I also build MCP servers using TypeScript and Spring AI, focusing on clean interfaces, composability, and real-world integration.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <h3 class="font-mono text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-accent);">
                Writing
              </h3>
              <p class="font-sans text-base" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: 1.5;">
                I like to write technical articles from time to time when I find something interesting or something that's worth sharing and could be helpful for others. You can find my articles in my medium account: <a href="https://medium.com/@techtopics/">techtopics</a>
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <h3 class="font-mono text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-accent);">
                Football & Chess
              </h3>
              <p class="font-sans text-base" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: 1.5;">
                I have been playing football regularly for over 10 years now and I also like to follow football matches and different leagues.
                Chess has also been an interest of me for a while, I have a rating of 1680 on chess.com.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Contact -->
        <section class="animate-fade-in delay-5">
          <h2 class="font-mono text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Let's Connect</h2>
          <div class="card">
            <p class="font-sans text-base mb-4" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: 1.5;">
              I'm always interested in new opportunities, collaborations, and conversations about
              technology. Feel free to reach out!
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
              <a
                href="mailto:tanbumails@gmail.com"
                class="btn"
              >
                Email Me
              </a>
              <a
                href="https://github.com/ANBU-THURAN"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="btn"
              >
                GitHub
              </a>
              <a
                href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/anbu-thuran/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="btn"
              >
                LinkedIn
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
